<br>
The problems are the towns in Luclin, till you get used to it: you can hardly move normally there on a low-end system.<br>
The trick is to turn plane clipping all the way down in towns, and look a bit down instead of straight forward. <br>
<br>
I also put the line UseUmbra=FALSE and UseTnL=FALSE in the eqclient.ini. Aided alot with zoning and the usetnl part aided a bit with performance.<br>
